The paper discusses the use of deep learning for single image super resolution in endomicroscopy, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of video registration techniques, which could fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the alignment of LR frames, which could fall under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
